<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>EXG — Sobre</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/exg.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="layout">
    <%- include('nav') %>
    <main class="page-content">

      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-logo">EXG</div>
        <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);margin-top:6px">
          Calculadora de Câmbio
        </div>
        <div class="about-desc">
          Aplicação para simulação de câmbio de moedas estrangeiras com cálculo automático
          de IOF, spread e taxa de serviço. Desenvolvida como trabalho acadêmico para a
          disciplina de Gerência de Configuração, Entrega e Integração Contínua.
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Equipe -->
      <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px">
        <div class="about-team-title">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"/></svg>
          Nossa Equipe
        </div>

        <div class="team-photo-placeholder">
          <img
            class="team-photo-img"
            src="/teamCFH.exg"
            alt="Equipe EXG"
            id="teamPhoto"
            onerror="this.style.display='none';document.getElementById('teamPlaceholder').style.display='flex'"
          >
          <div class="team-photo-placeholder-box" id="teamPlaceholder">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--border)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 4h-5L7 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v9a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3l-2.5-3z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="3"/></svg>
            <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600">Foto da Equipe</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;text-align:center;max-width:240px;color:var(--text-secondary)">
              Adicione o arquivo <code>teamCFH.exg</code> em <code>app/public/</code>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="team-grid">
            <div class="team-member">
              <div class="team-member-avatar">CC</div>
              <div class="team-member-name">Caio dos Santos Cunha</div>
              <div class="team-member-role">Desenvolvedor</div>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
              <div class="team-member-avatar">HP</div>
              <div class="team-member-name">Hugo Silva Pinheiro</div>
              <div class="team-member-role">Desenvolvedor</div>
            </div>
            <div class="team-member">
              <div class="team-member-avatar">FF</div>
              <div class="team-member-name">Fillipe Faria</div>
              <div class="team-member-role">Desenvolvedor</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Info Grid -->
      <div class="about-info-grid">
        <div class="about-info-card">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="about-info-label">Instituição</div>
            <div class="about-info-value">Escola Politécnica — PUC Campinas</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-info-card">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0 3-3h7z"/></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="about-info-label">Disciplina</div>
            <div class="about-info-value">Gerência de Configuração, Entrega e IC</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-info-card">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" x2="16" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="8" x2="8" y1="2" y2="6"/><line x1="3" x2="21" y1="10" y2="10"/></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="about-info-label">Período</div>
            <div class="about-info-value">1º Semestre 2026</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-info-card">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="about-info-label">Tecnologias</div>
            <div class="about-info-value">Node.js · TypeScript · React · Vite</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-info-card">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M10 2v7.527a2 2 0 0 1-.211.896L4.72 20.55a1 1 0 0 0 .9 1.45h12.76a1 1 0 0 0 .9-1.45l-5.069-10.127A2 2 0 0 1 14 9.527V2"/><path d="M8.5 2h7"/><path d="M7 16h10"/></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="about-info-label">Cobertura de Testes</div>
            <div class="about-info-value">100% (84 testes)</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-info-card">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"/><path d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"/><path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"/><path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"/></svg>
          <div>
            <div class="about-info-label">CI/CD</div>
            <div class="about-info-value">GitHub Actions</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
